public class ManagedConnectionFactoryImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.resource.spi.ManagedConnectionFactory

ManagedConnectionFactoryImpl implements javax.resource.spi.ManagedConnectionFactory interface. Accessors and mutators are provided for different properties which can be configured for the ManagedConnectionFactory instance.
